However , when the RcsC-YojN-RcsB system is activated by the presence of iron in a pmrA mutant , ugd expression is promoted by both RcsB and PhoP regulators in an RcsA-independent manner ( 30 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=15516559" target="_blank">15516559</a>]<br></label>
