<li>More recently , it was shown that leuO expression in E. coli can be activated by the RcsB and BglJ regulators ( 26 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=24659766" target="_blank">24659766</a>]<br></li>
