<li>For this purpose , the previously self-phosphor-ylated [ c - P ] - RcsCcyt-His6 or [ c - P ] - RcsDcyt-His6 was incu-32 32 bated with the purified RcsB response-regulator as detailed in Material and Methods .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=24023746" target="_blank">24023746</a>]<br></li>
