<li>RcsB represses fla-gellar motility and virulence genes on the Salmonella Pathogenicity Island II ( Gottesman et al. , 1985 ; Wang et al. , 2007 ) .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=27558204" target="_blank">27558204</a>]<br></li>
