<li>Besides the well-known ﬂagellar biosynthetic pathway , th more recently identiﬁed motility genes ( mcpC , STM3155 , yhjH , etc. [ 21 , 67 ] ) also were repressed by RcsB .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17905992" target="_blank">17905992</a>]<br></li>
