				<label class="TU_collapse_similarity" for="tu_similarity_27">
Positively regulated genes are those for which the transcription levels are elevated in an RcsB background or decreased in a rcsB background .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=17905992" target="_blank">17905992</a>]<br></label>
